      "content": "the house is just so quiet now. it’s like the air itself is heavy. i walk into the kitchen and i still expect to see him sitting there, but it’s just nothing. just empty space. i dont even know why i bother waking up and doing the dishes or making coffee when he isn't here to have any with me. everything feels so pointless.",
